---
title: Creamy Cannellini Bean & Veggie Pie with Mash Potato Top & Parsley
description: This easy-to-make veggie delux pie is a taste sensation. Seasoned cannellini beans and veggies in a pie is already a
great dinner, but bake the pie with a blanket of potato mash to create the top dinner just became a lot more exciting!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-cannellini-bean-veggie-pie-f1520650.jpg
